<title>VIETNAM: Vietnam fraudsters to face firing squad.</title>
<headline>Vietnam fraudsters to face firing squad.</headline>
<dateline>HANOI 1997-01-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>A court in Vietnam's southern Ho Chi Minh City sentenced two people to death on Tuesday at the end of a showcase fraud trial.</p>
<p>A court official told Reuters by phone that Pham Minh Tong and Nguyen Ngoc Tan had been found guilty of fraudulent appropriation of citizens' property and would be executed by firing squad.</p>
